tried a human you see a group near the

07:49.919 --> 07:51.759
surface splashing around in a way that

07:51.759 --> 07:53.520
doesn't make sense one of them drifts

07:53.520 --> 07:55.360
too far from the rest too far to get

07:55.360 --> 07:56.960
pulled back in time if something were to

07:56.960 --> 07:59.039
happen so you circle once from below

07:59.039 --> 08:01.039
once from the side a little closer each

08:01.039 --> 08:02.800
time until they pause and look around

