they panic the deeper you pull them you

08:24.000 --> 08:25.919
hold steady while their arms flail and

08:25.919 --> 08:27.680
the last burst of air slips from their

08:27.680 --> 08:29.360
mouth in a string of bubbles that drift

08:29.360 --> 08:31.120
back toward the surface they manage to

08:31.120 --> 08:32.959
twist free but only for a second you

08:32.959 --> 08:34.880
grab their foot drag again and this time

08:34.880 --> 08:36.880
they stop fighting then you let go they

08:36.880 --> 08:38.479
shoot upward and scream before they

